msgid "Hotkey:   :kbd:`Ctrl-LMB`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/selecting/tools.rst:123
msgid "Lasso select is used by drawing a dotted line around vertices or the origin of the objects, in *Object Mode*."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/selecting/tools.rst:126
msgid "While holding :kbd:`Ctrl` down, you simply have to draw around the points you want to select with :kbd:`LMB`."
msgstr ""

